{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/684680/extras/Discord.gif?t=1725480426\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Test your reflexes in POLYGONEER, defend yourself from prolygonal shapes taht comes from everywhere, just hitting is not enough you need to match the right color shot to the polygon too! Are you ready for the challenge? </li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/684680/extras/01.gif?t=1725480426\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Perfect to play when you want to test or improve your reflexes, or while you are on a queue for another game, this is a small and replayable game. The objectives are to beat the 5 stages, get on top of the leaderboards, unlock achievements and beat personal scores and times. </li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/684680/extras/02.gif?t=1725480426\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Test your reflex destroying the enemies using the right color shot in one of the 5 levels (or in the hidden HELL level if you're brave enough)<br></li><li>Get bigger scores by not missing any shot, the multiplier increase for every 5 enemies destroyed. If you miss the color or the shot the multiplier return to zero.</li></ul><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/684680/extras/03.gif?t=1725480426\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fast paced arcade gameplay.<br></li><li>5 different stages and a hidden hell stage.<br></li><li>Leaderboards for each stage.<br></li><li>Polygonal graphics.<br></li><li>Great to play both with joystick or keyboard.<br></li><li>6 Amazing electro-hardcore original tracks.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Level 1 15 seconds","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/684680/c72187e06de3467ae898a6b717979a5d95a0f424.jpg"},{"name":"Level 1